channel.description:
Hello and im searching for people to work with me on a 517 server, So far i've got:
[b]All basic things All skills Tutorial at the beginning f2p quests 100%!!!! and the basicly member quests like monkey madness and lost city. Slayer [LIKE RS ONE]!! Magic 100% Range + gfx + projectile 100% Ava have to do quest to get. Alot of bosses to battle with! And you don't have commands like ::home or ::master, you have to walk from city to city and you have to train your combat. xp is 250xp a hit. Pest control 100%!!! trust me duel arena 100% clan wars, bh, and all the noob things 100% Almost all bugs & glitchs are fixed This is the best server in the history.[/b]
I made it bymyself and only bymyself, but i want some ppl to join as beta tester or website programmer.
[b]Pictures will be there in an hour or so.[/b]

item.title: [NO NAME] 517 server development
item.dc:creator: @the1337legend the1337legend
item.description:
@the1337legend wrote:

[quote=“zyle1992, post:9, topic:313710”][quote author=the1337legend link=topic=410217.msg3026978#msg3026978 date=1258073051]

What the FUCK is a 517?

slang for 508 loading 525 cache… 8-25 = 17, 517
[/quote]

8 - 25 = -17. 525 - 17 = 508. So technically, the median of a 508 loading 525 cache would be a 516.5
Then why don’t we call 317’s 347’s? 99% of all 317’s load 377 cache, 77-17 = 60 / 2 = 30, 317 + 30 = 347. And even then, most cache’s today are edited with a bunch of 474+ bullshit. So they’re probably closer to 451, according to your logic.[/quote]

People call them 317’s because 99% of people are ‘retards’ and don’t know they’re loading a 377 cache. they assume ‘317’ is a ‘317’ nothing more.

and that was just random tbh, but every since someone said they released a ‘517’ server, it was a 508 loading 525, he called it 517, nao everyone is, so w.e
